<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to Duelingpets.net, <%= @user.vname %></h1>
    <p>
      The kid friendly website welcomes you to huge gangs
      of fun. Explore the stories, artwork, and pets, this
      wonderful community has created for your benefit.
      Please feel free to contribute as well, and have tons
      of fun in the forums. The many users of this site will
      be happy to greet you and welcome you with open arms.
    </p>
    <p>
      You have successfully signed up to Duelingpets.net,
      your login id is: <%= @user.login_id %>.<br>
    </p>
    <p>
      In order to activate your account for the first time
      please be sure to use this token: <%= @accounttoken %>
      in the Verify link below the login screen. Once you
      have activated your account you may login normally.
    </p>
    <p>
      To login to the site, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>
